title: Pod Save America Takes Seattle
description: Jon, Jon, Tommy, and Dan hold a live show at Seattle’s Showbox SoDo Theater, where they’re joined by Washington Governor Jay Inslee to talk health care, activism, and the future of Democratic Party.
author: hey@crooked.com (Crooked Media)
